{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You wouldn't put a-- a civilian in because you didn't know whether he was German or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were always very proud of their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody wore uniforms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except it was important then to know who is important, namely which uniform means what?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "SS.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the SS!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You knew there was a secret police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You certainly didn't want to run into them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had to learn, because there were so many different uniforms with so many different signs here on the collar or the medals, whatever they wore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So by the time I know-- I knew who was who, it was too late to make a difference.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It didn't make any difference anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Holland was a country-- one of the richest in Europe because of the colonies which it still had then.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans took their time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They plundered much faster in other countries than in Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It took quite some time before they really made beasts out of themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they were-- they didn't-- they didn't interfere for a while, let's say that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't interfere with one's so-called normal life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I changed then to another-- as I said, the Hollandsche Schouwburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the restrictions, the first restrictions, they did very softly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Came about, I think, 17 months into the invasion before they really started to be heard and to be seen all over the place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Once the restrictions started-- and there were every week practically, or perhaps every day different ones-- it became very, very rough.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Slowly but surely, first the Jews were not allowed to visit, let's say, coffee houses and restaurants, or movies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Jewish artists were not allowed to work anywhere but in one theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The painters were not allowed to exhibit.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
